@startuml ReportAppSlideDiagram
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #4B5563
skinparam DefaultFontName Arial
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam backgroundColor white

title Report App - Presentation Diagram

actor Maker
actor Checker

rectangle "Frontend\nAngular SPA" as FE #D5E8D4 {
  component "Login + Report UI" as UI
  component "JWT Interceptor" as JWT
}

rectangle "Backend\nSpring Boot API" as BE #FFF2CC {
  component "Auth APIs" as Auth
  component "Report APIs" as ReportApi
  component "Workflow Service\nReportRunService" as Workflow
  component "Audit Service" as Audit
  component "Excel Export Service" as Export
}

database "H2 Database" as DB #F8CECC
folder "Excel Templates" as TPL #E1D5E7

rectangle "Core Business Records" as DOMAIN #FFFFFF {
  entity "Report" as Report
  entity "ReportRun" as ReportRun
  entity "ReportAuditEvent" as AuditEvent
  entity "User" as User
}

Maker --> UI : login / execute / submit
Checker --> UI : login / review / decide
UI --> JWT : attach token
JWT --> Auth : POST /auth/login
JWT --> ReportApi : authenticated API calls

ReportApi --> Workflow : execute / submit / decide / query
Workflow --> Audit : record events
Workflow --> DB : read/write runs
Auth --> DB : read users
ReportApi --> DB : read report definitions
Export --> DB : read snapshot / report data
Export --> TPL : render xlsx

DB --> User
DB --> Report
DB --> ReportRun
DB --> AuditEvent

Report --> ReportRun : one-to-many
ReportRun --> AuditEvent : one-to-many
User --> ReportRun : maker/checker
User --> AuditEvent : actor

note right of Workflow
Business heart of the system:
- enforces maker-checker workflow
- stores run snapshots
- manages status transitions
end note

note bottom of ReportApi
Main architectural risk:
report SQL is executed directly.
end note

@enduml
